      <title>SCMP报告说，中国披露了强大的深海电缆切割机</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-22/china-discloses-powerful-deep-sea-cable-cutter-scmp-reports</link>
      <description><![CDATA[《南方晨报》报道，中国首次透露，它首次开发了一种紧凑的深海切割设备，该设备足以实现严重的通信线路。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-22/china-discloses-powerful-deep-sea-cable-cutter-scmp-reports</guid>
      <pubDate>Sat, 22 Mar 2025 06:45:31 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>日本，中国，韩国相遇随着美国关税压力的上升</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-22/japan-china-south-korea-meet-as-us-tariff-pressure-rises</link>
      <description><![CDATA[日本，中国和韩国的外交大臣周六在东京举行了三边谈判，试图进一步合作，并为潜在的领导峰会奠定了基础，因为这些国家面临经济破坏并加剧了全球政治紧张局势。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-22/japan-china-south-korea-meet-as-us-tariff-pressure-rises</guid>
      <pubDate>Sat, 22 Mar 2025 04:07:37 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>特朗普撤销了拜登，哈里斯，眨眼的安全许可</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-22/trump-revokes-security-clearances-for-biden-harris-blinken</link>
      <description><![CDATA[美国总统唐纳德·特朗普（Donald Trump）撤销了前总统乔·拜登（Joe Biden）及其政府的一些主要成员的安全许可，称他们继续访问机密信息“不再符合国家利益”。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-22/trump-revokes-security-clearances-for-biden-harris-blinken</guid>
      <pubDate>Sat, 22 Mar 2025 02:16:24 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>卡尼（Carney）推出了加拿大关税的救济，“国家建设”改革</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-22/carney-unveils-canada-tariff-relief-nation-building-reforms</link>
      <description><![CDATA[加拿大总理马克·卡尼（Mark Carney）宣布了一系列旨在削弱美国关税的痛苦以及“建立国家建设”改革的措施，以促进贸易和投资的日子，然后他预计将举行选举。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-22/carney-unveils-canada-tariff-relief-nation-building-reforms</guid>
      <pubDate>Sat, 22 Mar 2025 01:37:02 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>特朗普剥夺了居住在美国的532,000名移民的法律地位</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-22/trump-to-strip-legal-status-from-532-000-migrants-living-in-us</link>
      <description><![CDATA[根据周五在联邦公报上发布的通知，特朗普政府将撤销可能有超过50万移民从合法进入美国的移民的临时法律地位。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-22/trump-to-strip-legal-status-from-532-000-migrants-living-in-us</guid>
      <pubDate>Sat, 22 Mar 2025 00:24:16 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>萨斯喀彻温省敦促卡尼应对中国关税的威胁</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-21/saskatchewan-urges-carney-to-deal-with-threat-of-chinese-tariffs</link>
      <description><![CDATA[萨斯喀彻温省总理斯科特·莫伊（Scott Moe）表示，中国对低油菜籽的关税是对加拿大西部经济的“最直接威胁”。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-21/saskatchewan-urges-carney-to-deal-with-threat-of-chinese-tariffs</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 21 Mar 2025 21:59:12 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>社会保障负责人在法院命令后取消关闭机构</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-21/doge-ruling-shouldn-t-stop-social-security-payouts-judge-says</link>
      <description><![CDATA[联邦法官说，限制埃隆·马斯克（Elon Musk）及其成本降低团队的数据访问的命令不适用于代理商员工，社会保障局的代理负责人撤退了他关闭办公室的威胁。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-21/doge-ruling-shouldn-t-stop-social-security-payouts-judge-says</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 21 Mar 2025 20:28:58 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>秘密拜登交易允许雪佛龙支付委内瑞拉百万美元</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-21/biden-s-secret-deal-allowed-chevron-to-pay-venezuela-millions</link>
      <description><![CDATA[据知情人士说，拜登政府秘密允许雪佛龙公司向委内瑞拉政府支付数亿美元，尽管许可证明确禁止此类支出。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-21/biden-s-secret-deal-allowed-chevron-to-pay-venezuela-millions</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 21 Mar 2025 19:47:03 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>由于移植案，美国阿根廷的柯克纳（Argentina）的基尔奇纳（Kirchner）进入</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-21/us-bars-argentina-s-kirchner-from-entry-due-to-graft-conviction</link>
      <description><![CDATA[美国政府禁止前阿根廷总统克里斯蒂娜·费尔南德斯·德·基尔奇纳（Cristina Fernandez de Kirchner）及其直系亲属由于她的腐败定罪而进入该国，这一举动势必使该国今年晚些时候的中期选举两极分化。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-21/us-bars-argentina-s-kirchner-from-entry-due-to-graft-conviction</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 21 Mar 2025 19:42:19 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
